<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19819005?v=4" alt="code dev avatar" style="max-width: 100px; border-radius: 50%; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        <h2 class="color-primary" style="color: #007BFF;">{{subject}}</h2>
        <hr/>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Please use the URL below to verify your account <br/> This link is valid for 24 hours</p>

        <a href={{link}} class="btn-link" style="background-color: #007BFF; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Verify Account</a>

        <p style="margin-bottom: 50px;">If you didn't create an account, you can ignore this email</p>

        <hr/>
        <p>Regards,</p>
        <p><b>Anton Authkit</b></p>
        <div>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem;">
                If you are having trouble clicking the "Verify Account" button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser
                <br/>
                <a href="{{link}}">{{link}}</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>